messages.messageBody:
Good Morning Folks!

Yesterday our family had scheduled an improptu skateboarding day at
Sammamish Park, WA
We had a wonderful sunny day at the skateboarding park in Sammamish.
We met new folks and that was fun. A few people asked in the home-
schooling boards we subscribe to, if we can do this activity again..
YES, WE CAN!!! After making a few calls, this is what we have to
offer for all homeschoolers / unschoolers. This is not part of any
group. We are just going to have clean safe fun.

Friday, March 6th 1-3pm @ Renton Skatebarn $5 per kid. The famous
Mitchie Brusco (utube him and you will be either amazed or clench
your teeth with fear!) will be there to skate with us! Skatebarn's
address is: 2900 Lind Ave SW
Renton, WA 98057


Friday, March 20th 1pm @ Sammamish Skatepark if we have a no rain day
OR snow! Sammamish address is: 801 228th Ave SE Sammamish, WA 98075

Hope to see you there! If you have any questions, you can email me @
sherylshomler@...
